{"tid":1697294,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我地公佈美國製催淚彈各種化學成份用途！fact check 最緊要搵reference！以正視聽！","createTime":"2019-11-06T18:14:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T10:01:22.000Z","uid":1806,"like":133,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"811e98fe5cdb1dbcabe72daeaee0fccbe4d61b7d","tid":1697294,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T18:14:10.000Z","msg":"近日有人流傳美國催淚彈有矽粉，碳粉，更有可能有砂糖。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香城教育電視(HKGETV)近日接到查詢，本著為市民提供真相。於是係我地係資料庫中找回警方用的美國製催淚彈型號為為MP-6M5-CS的安全性數據表(MSDS)，該MSDS指出催淚彈除左含有CS為有效成份外，還包含多種化學品。<br />\nDocument Link: <a href=\"http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/pdf/SDS/SDS-MP-6M5-CS.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nonlethaltechnologies.com%2Fpdf%2FSDS%2FSDS-MP-6M5-CS.pdf&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=9a97818e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/pdf/SDS/SDS-MP-6M5-CS.pdf</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iktV6X3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiktV6X3.png&h=f3f04131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每種化合物都有他們的用途:</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">[(2-Chlorophenyl)methylene]malononitrile 又名「2-chlorobenzalmalononitrile」或簡稱「CS」</span></strong><br />\n作為催淚彈主要成份。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Nickel </span></strong>為化學元素之一，其Nickel Powder本身是易燃及有爆炸危險的化學物質，在此用作為催淚彈入面的火藥之一，順帶一提，如發生跟Nickel powder有關的火災，絕不可以直接用水弄熄火源,因為Nickel跟水會發生化學反應，並產生爆炸性的氣體 - 氫氣 Hydrogen。不過，在此催淚彈情況下，只佔少於百分之一，而且大多在發射時亦已用盡，不必擔心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其中<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Aluminum powder, Zirconium powder(還原劑) 可以跟Potassium Perchlorate,Barium chromate(氧化劑)</span></strong>形成閃光粉(flash powder)。閃光粉除了會用來製作煙花外，而且更用來燃燒CS從而令CS更快更易去擴散。<br />\n在一份專利文件: US14/711980，不同比例的閃光粉(文件中的Slurry Composition)更會影響CS擴散的效率及時間。<br />\n<br />\nNotable Trace Components (&lt;0.1% w/w)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Lead 2,4,6-trinitro-m-phenylene dioxide / lead styphnate</span></strong><br />\n主要用於軍事和商業用途的小型武器彈藥入面作為主要爆藥，用作槍械入面的推進劑，<br />\n它在簡單的衝擊下不會點燃。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Magnesium Oxide，Magnesium Carbonate</span></strong>暫時<br />\n未有實際証據有任何用途，基於這兩隻化合物特性，大膽推斷用來隔熱用途。我地團隊會繼續<br />\n尋找相關資源。<br />\n<br />\n由於我地未能係MSDS找到有碳，沙塘，矽，所以未能知道網上流傳消息的真偽。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">如想支持我地既工作，可以透過</span></span></strong><br />\n<blockquote>Buy me a coffee捐款（以美金結算）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<a href=\"https://www.buymeacoffee.com/hkgetv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buymeacoffee.com%2Fhkgetv&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=70267b48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.buymeacoffee.com/hkgetv</a><br />\n或<br />\n眾籌連結（以港幣結算）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<a href=\"https://goget.fund/2MOT9co\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoget.fund%2F2MOT9co&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=810ff67b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goget.fund/2MOT9co</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"cad6e1c6f9c5a9b9ab591715358fbf4f92faed74","tid":1697294,"uid":17220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T18:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e066f647c45d108755eb45eb15eba6f0c88ebb","tid":1697294,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T18:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695bbdd36318a19570d16c8bf6e8ff99162fcd95","tid":1697294,"uid"